message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "ego-mol-llm: Blind structure prediction from molecular-network ego neighborhoods"
version: 0.1.0
date-released: "2026-07-21"
license: Apache-2.0
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Contributors
    name: ego-mol-llm
repository-code: "https://github.com/arome-science/ego-mol-llm"
abstract: >
  Open-source toolkit for blind molecular structure prediction of unknown
  MS/MS features from GraphML molecular-network ego neighborhoods using
  chemistry LLMs (ChemDFM / Qwen).
keywords:
  - metabolomics
  - mass spectrometry
  - molecular networking
  - chemistry LLM
  - structure elucidation
